high_descs: Turn to your right  walk toward the stove then turn right  and face the counter
Pick up the spoon on the counter beside the bread
Turn to your right then head to the sink to your left
Put the spoon in the sink then rinse it
Turn to your right walk forward head to the microwave
Put the spoon on the left side of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the clean spoon on the left side of the microwave

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the counter directly to the left of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Carry the spoon to the kitchen sink.
Place the spoon in the right side of the sink, turn on the water, wash the spoon, and remove it from the sink.
Carry the spoon to the microwave cart.
Place the spoon on the cart to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed spoon to the microwave cart.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the spin behind the pan on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the spoon in the sink and then pick the washed spoon up.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the black dresser.
Place the spoon to the left of the microwave on the black dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon to the left of the microwave on the black dresser.
